{"tid":1907231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中信出售麥當勞中港業務22%權益　總代價逾5億美元！","createTime":"2020-03-02T12:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T19:00:20.000Z","uid":63113,"like":137,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8bdc1e78e925064d2f98dc04f9b7dada645539","tid":1907231,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6368abe216993680f75619429d9a579485b813","tid":1907231,"uid":63113,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"中信股份向中信資本作為一般合伙人新設立的基金出售Fast Food Holdings的42.31%股權，連同一筆股東貸款，總出售代價5.33億美元。Fast Food Holdings目前持有麥當勞中國大陸及香港業務52%權益。換言之，今次交易涉及約22%麥當勞中港業務權益。<br />\n<br />\n交易完成後，中信股份在Fast Food Holdings的股權降至19.23%，相當於約10%麥當勞中港業務權益。中信表示，今次出售為中信股份實現投資價值，將繼續通過持有剩餘的麥當勞股權參與未來發展。<br />\n<br />\n較早時，北京產權交易所產權轉讓資料披露，中信以掛牌方式出售Fast Food Holdings的42.31%股權。中信表示，交易純屬商業決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512051-20200302.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512051-20200302.htm&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=31d6c42f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512051-20200302.htm&h=83974579\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512051-20200302.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e0e7f795c363b017e8d59b971f4c001e87e86756","tid":1907231,"uid":84102,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"車喱"},{"pid":"8ef3310ab5d5c154419887120f8023747a4867fe","tid":1907231,"uid":228995,"like":205,"dislike":4,"score":201,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"左手交右手？"},{"pid":"43db92505d5a817f764fca68199a402ec1a5e511","tid":1907231,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ce71e21